{"tid":1627754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果港島咁危險 不如比和理非用","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T02:11:19.000Z","uid":94771,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f8c85032d0cf560e2d9b42c555e0e34278062c","tid":1627754,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:33:52.000Z","msg":"第一和理非只要人數多就唔太怕狗<br />\n人數愈多 信心愈大 而且都唔需要勇武保護<br />\n<br />\n如果狗單方面出催淚彈 咁就又和理非自己散<br />\n咁和理非就影到張黑警打散和平遊行的相 和理非都叫完成任務<br />\n而且和理非因為其左膠性質　所以黑警係唔會可以引起事端<br />\n因為和理非［死忍能力］極強<br />\n<br />\n就算和理非被捕 個罪名都一定細好多<br />\n因為一定入唔到暴動，頂多都係非法集結，蒙面法。<br />\n加上初犯，好大機會都唔洗入去坐<br />\n<br />\n所以如果港島遊行最好交比和理非　勇武就係自己區各地開花<br />\n我認為依個安排比較靈活<br />\n<br />\n一　勇武轉打遊擊　根本唔需要和理非係後面Cover，和理非係遊擊現場只會係拖累<br />\n二　令和理非唔太需要怕黑警<br />\n三　和理非自己拎到想要的光環相<br />\n四　輿論影響比較好<br />\n五　因為和理非人數眾多，令到狗要派重兵係港島，周邊地區好難處理，間接幫佐勇武手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e85965ca4d5951873f53c79017d59bfb8ba203","tid":1627754,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZbHc1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZbHc1d.jpg&h=6c8e3b17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8edc485b099f57eb635ad1a972f7c27ba7341f4","tid":1627754,"uid":236281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1ZhMhv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1ZhMhv.jpg&h=128ca870&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e49dd57897a7586cf284e137f79379e55f6707dc","tid":1627754,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DoFdjGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDoFdjGh.jpg&h=6443758a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf820a799